---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import PageNav from "../components/PageNav.astro";
---

<Layout title="Productividad: Tecnología Punta Propia">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="mb-8 md:mb-16 text-center animate-fade-in">
    <h1 class="font-body font-extrabold text-3xl md:text-6xl text-primary tracking-tight mb-4 md:mb-6 animate-slide-up" style="animation-delay: 0s; opacity: 0;">
      Productividad: <br/><span class="text-on-surface-variant font-light">Tecnología Punta Propia</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="font-body text-lg text-on-surface-variant max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed animate-slide-up" style="animation-delay: 0.1s; opacity: 0;">
      Un modelo sistémico de síntesis intelectual donde la sabiduría colectiva se transmuta en soberanía técnica mediante flujos de transformación y regulación.
    </p>
  </section>

  <!-- Diagram Canvas -->
  <section class="relative py-4 md:py-12 mb-8 md:mb-16">
    <!-- Los Nodos -->
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-6 md:gap-12 relative z-10">
      <!-- Node 1: Sabiduría Popular -->
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center group animate-slide-up" style="animation-delay: 0.1s; opacity: 0;">
        <div class="w-32 h-32 md:w-64 md:h-64 rounded-full bg-surface-container-highest flex items-center justify-center relative overflow-hidden transition-all duration-500 group-hover:scale-105 group-hover:shadow-xl border-4 border-primary/20">
          <img class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-80 mix-blend-multiply" alt="Sabiduría Popular" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuAi_xycHgbABOV3uZTUta7kGPv3pm7vgun1ddwa2F-t5LWmPfYj1MeDoJitkDffCndydP3LtJn7nHkAOU1WEpGLuiQ5niwCFxpEtEJsqbfqeog1vv5h8Uu8o7stNnU-QsUyKn5zaI4zWifghSiI-Dxb_qH1M-EH1iLCYc1f-ZMVuLOkS97AnLXixCNChGc0r4pyCfiSA_6TJ64QrvaJtXotpnnyYHs3-WA4hPQ9ZOvMYuUEGqrKPfFxDDmiwub2zdwrsqU_yVMLKHg-"/>
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-primary/20 to-transparent"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-3 md:mt-6 text-center">
          <h3 class="font-body font-bold text-sm md:text-lg text-primary uppercase tracking-widest">Sabiduría Popular</h3>
          <div class="mt-2 flex items-center justify-center gap-2 text-on-surface-variant">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">trending_flat</span>
            <span class="font-body text-xs uppercase tracking-tighter">Hacia Tecnología Propia</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Central Vortex Transition -->
      <div class="hidden md:flex flex-col items-center text-outline-variant">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl animate-pulse">sync_alt</span>
        <span class="font-body text-[10px] uppercase mt-2 tracking-[0.2em]">Transformación</span>
      </div>

      <!-- Node 2: Software de la Manera (CENTRAL) -->
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center group mt-0 md:-mt-12 animate-slide-up" style="animation-delay: 0.2s; opacity: 0;">
        <div class="w-40 h-40 md:w-80 md:h-80 rounded-full bg-surface-container-lowest border-4 border-primary flex items-center justify-center relative overflow-hidden shadow-2xl transition-all duration-500 group-hover:scale-110">
          <img class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-90" alt="Software de la Manera" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuCIWVa1MdR-xtpqjH3JTDDX4Gr6KfbA7mGJVzYg0Ukj3gMuZePeJ22bSsJpab0jhal-wU3T9sZKcMPclBN_7ryfvJ62kj6yEyZzOqjR8OtQ3tm6xvpJMYLn3lXKzahwe971fdrsdVUQxO7UfqhBYgEEzdrCc6yAwanKj7e3O41biqevcVK9y-4xl2OeeknedIA0_-tyGidMpNkzoSfrWrCc07w98_5akwFzCH78qA2U5abBCgPtQYiXrrpeE6ou65QPbCPWc9ZLMuVc"/>
          <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center">
            <div class="w-full h-full bg-primary/5 absolute"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-6 text-center">
          <span class="inline-block px-4 py-1 rounded-full bg-primary text-on-primary font-body text-[10px] uppercase mb-3">Núcleo Central</span>
          <h3 class="font-body font-extrabold text-xl md:text-2xl text-on-surface tracking-tight uppercase">Software de la Manera</h3>
          <div class="mt-2 flex items-center justify-center gap-2 text-primary font-bold">
            <span class="font-body text-sm">Tecnología Punta Propia</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Central Vortex Transition -->
      <div class="hidden md:flex flex-col items-center text-outline-variant">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl animate-pulse" style="animation-delay: 0.3s;">published_with_changes</span>
        <span class="font-body text-[10px] uppercase mt-2 tracking-[0.2em]">Regulación</span>
      </div>

      <!-- Node 3: Software del Modo -->
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center group mt-4 md:mt-0 animate-slide-up" style="animation-delay: 0.4s; opacity: 0;">
        <div class="w-32 h-32 md:w-64 md:h-64 rounded-full bg-surface-container-highest flex items-center justify-center relative overflow-hidden transition-all duration-500 group-hover:scale-105 group-hover:shadow-xl border-4 border-tertiary/20">
          <img class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-80 mix-blend-multiply" alt="Software del Modo" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuC2c0-AVLIQiViqO69oIdIJt5nEWHgffPMybK0u4gVQLn4jZOBGXkYd1y6VZynSgsHqIaRNq08PtysIIeAFfqxrWidieXRtjydpZTwTFDc6XIKK6XvNkV7Ab5hNQlMTq7UgHgP18bZt8CsaRx3NEqVY90V4VVHwtRhYpW2DRskMafBI0M9D_xi9oshF3Q6euMsCmiG_AbsLR38IBWrQBOrTe6ynXGf-DFDdIFVYNFvqX3PiA82MeArhSDzTup3R-Fgtv1Sg_lcKvhxf"/>
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-tertiary/20 to-transparent"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-6 text-center">
          <h3 class="font-body font-bold text-lg text-tertiary uppercase tracking-widest">Software del Modo</h3>
          <div class="mt-2 flex items-center justify-center gap-2 text-on-surface-variant">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">move_down</span>
            <span class="font-body text-xs uppercase tracking-tighter">Transferencia Punta</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Technical Cards Bento Grid -->
  <section class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-16">
    <div class="glass-card p-8 rounded-[2rem] transition-all hover:bg-white animate-slide-up" style="animation-delay: 0.5s; opacity: 0;">
      <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-primary-container flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-on-primary-container">psychology</span>
      </div>
      <h4 class="font-body font-bold text-primary mb-3">Síntesis Intelectual</h4>
      <p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">
        La transmutación del conocimiento empírico en algoritmos de precisión, garantizando que el "saber hacer" popular se convierta en "poder hacer" técnico.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="glass-card p-8 rounded-[2rem] transition-all hover:bg-white scale-105 z-20 border border-primary-fixed-dim/30 animate-slide-up" style="animation-delay: 0.6s; opacity: 0;">
      <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-secondary-container flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-on-secondary-container">account_tree</span>
      </div>
      <h4 class="font-body font-bold text-secondary mb-3">Flujo Circular</h4>
      <p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">
        Un bucle de retroalimentación donde la Regulación y la Transformación actúan como fuerzas centrípetas que mantienen la cohesión del ecosistema técnico.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="glass-card p-8 rounded-[2rem] transition-all hover:bg-white animate-slide-up" style="animation-delay: 0.7s; opacity: 0;">
      <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-tertiary-container flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-on-tertiary-container">settings_input_component</span>
      </div>
      <h4 class="font-body font-bold text-tertiary mb-3">Soberanía Técnica</h4>
      <p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">
        La capacidad de generar tecnología punta desde el núcleo propio, eliminando la dependencia externa y fomentando la transferencia horizontal.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Footer Section -->
  <section class="pt-12 border-t border-outline-variant/20 animate-slide-up" style="animation-delay: 0.8s; opacity: 0;">
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-12">
      <div class="flex-1">
        <h2 class="font-body text-2xl md:text-3xl font-extrabold text-on-surface mb-6 tracking-tight animate-slide-up" style="animation-delay: 0.9s; opacity: 0;">Dinámica de Productividad Social</h2>
        <p class="font-body text-on-surface-variant mb-4 animate-slide-up" style="animation-delay: 1s; opacity: 0;">
          Este modelo representa el ciclo vital de la innovación en contextos de soberanía. No es un proceso lineal, sino un vórtice de crecimiento donde cada interacción entre la <strong>Sabiduría Popular</strong> y el <strong>Software de la Manera</strong> reinforce el tejido productivo del ecosistema.
        </p>
        <div class="flex gap-4 mt-8 flex-wrap animate-slide-up" style="animation-delay: 1.1s; opacity: 0;">
          <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-surface-container-highest rounded text-[10px] font-body uppercase text-on-surface-variant">Metodología V.24</span>
          <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-surface-container-highest rounded text-[10px] font-body uppercase text-on-surface-variant">Sostenibilidad Técnica</span>
          <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-surface-container-highest rounded text-[10px] font-body uppercase text-on-surface-variant">Código Abierto</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex-1 glass-card p-8 rounded-xl border border-white/40 animate-slide-up" style="animation-delay: 1.2s; opacity: 0;">
        <h5 class="font-body font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest text-primary mb-4">Notas Técnicas</h5>
        <ul class="space-y-4 text-xs text-on-surface-variant font-body">
          <li class="flex gap-3">
            <span class="text-primary font-bold">01.</span>
            <span>La "Tecnología Punta Propia" se define por su capacidad de adaptación cultural y eficiencia termodinámica.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-3">
            <span class="text-primary font-bold">02.</span>
            <span>El vórtice de transición minimiza la pérdida de información durante la codificación del saber popular.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-3">
            <span class="text-primary font-bold">03.</span>
            <span>La transferencia de tecnología punta debe ser bidireccional para mantener la homeostasis del sistema social.</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <PageNav
    prev={{ href: "/practica-pervivencia", label: "Práctica de Pervivencia", sublabel: "Productividad" }}
    next={{ href: "/reciclaje-cibernetico", label: "Reciclaje", sublabel: "Cibernético" }}
  />
</Layout>